          "_name": "features5",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"features5\" group=\"Features\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\" plugins=\"mobirise-icons2\">\n\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"9\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"9\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showsubTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Card Color\" name=\"cardColor\" value=\"#fafafa\" condition=\"showLink\" selected>\n\n        <select title=\"Columns\" name=\"columns\">\n            <option value=\"3\">4</option>\n            <option value=\"4\">3</option>\n            <option value=\"6\">2</option>\n            <option value=\"12\" selected>1</option>\n        </select>\n\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"../_images/background3.jpg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#a5cf61\" selected>\n            <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"../_images/background13.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.5\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\">\n    </div>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row\">\n            <div class=\"item features-without-image mb-4 col-12 col-md-{{columns}}\">\n                <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n                    <div class=\"row\">\n                        <div class=\"col-12 col-md-7\">\n                            <div class=\"text-wrapper\">\n                                <h6 class=\"card-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-2\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" mbr-if=\"showsubTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-subtitle\"></h6>\n                                <h5 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-1\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title\"><b>KIT FOTOVOLTAICO</b><br><b>DA BALCONE</b><br><b><br></b></h5>\n                                <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mb-5\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">Non hai possibilità di installare un tradizionale fotovoltaico?<br><br> Abiti in un condominio o non hai gli spazi adatti?<br><br>Niente Panico, perché ti offriamo una soluzione.<br><br><b>Il nostro Kit Fotovoltaico da Balcone!<br></b><br>Analizziamo e studiamo l'esposizione del tuo balcone&nbsp; ed insieme progettiamo il <b>tuo mini-fotovoltaico.&nbsp;</b><br><br>Vuoi saperne di più ed iniziare a risparmiare ?</p>\n                                <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" class=\"mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\"><a href=\"page1.html#contacts2-h\" class=\"btn btn-primary\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\"><span class=\"mobi-mbri mobi-mbri-info mbr-iconfont mbr-iconfont-btn\"></span>Contattaci&nbsp;</a></div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"col-12 col-md-5\">\n                            <div class=\"img-wrapper\">\n                                <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/ftv20balcone-982x655.png\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\">\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            \n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
